title: Onnx export: segmentation fault
body_html:
When I try to run the onnx export tutorial from here (http://pytorch.org/tutorials/advanced/super_resolution_with_caffe2.html#transfering-srresnet-using-onnx) everything works fine.
When i try to do it like here (https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/blob/master/docs/source/onnx.rst) I get a segmentation fault
For everything else torchvision is working perfectly
